====Key Shortcuts====

* {{key|Y}} - Confirm the current temporary path
* {{key|N}} - discard the current temporary path
* {{key|F}} - Finish a path
* {{key|C}} - Cancel a path
* {{key|Esc}} - Abandon search
* {{key|G}} - Select (Group) the path nearest to the mouse pointer


* {{key|S}} -Toggle cursor snapping: If enable, the plugin will automatically move the cursor to the brightest voxel within the specified x,y,z snapping window <sup>1</sup>.
* {{key|M}} - Finds the brightest voxel (maximum) above and below the current x,y position and automatically clicks on it.<sup>1</sup>.
<div class="floatright"><sup>1</sup> If multiple maxima exist, their average positioning is used.</div>


* {{key|+}} - Zoom in (Simultaneously on all views)
* {{key|-}} - Zoom out (Simultaneously on all views)
* {{key|Shift}} - Synchronizes XY, ZY and XZ views while moving the cursor
* {{key|5}} - Toggle ''View paths'' choice: ''Parts in nearby slices'' / ''Projected through all slices''
* {{key|V}} - View all traced paths as lines in a new image stack


